content: {"name": "We Are Not Afraid Community Resource Center Polo Grounds", "alternate_name": "", "description": "You can register in person on Mondays at 12PM.\n\u2022 Please bring any type of photo ID (can be expired) and proof of address (piece of mail; medical card; school ID) for you and each person in your household.\n\u2022 Without proof, we will give out groceries only to household members present in person.", "email": "", "url": "https://www.wanacommunitycenter.org/ew-food-programs", "status": "active", "address": {"address_1": "2965 Frederick Douglass Blvd", "address_2": null, "city": "New York", "state_province": "NY", "postal_code": "10039", "country": "US"}, "location": {"latitude": 40.830784, "longitude": -73.937332}, "phones": [{"number": "(332) 867-9965", "type": "voice"}], "regular_schedule": [{"weekday": "Monday", "opens_at": "17:00", "closes_at": "19:00"}], "service_attributes": [{"attribute_key": "REQUIREMENT", "attribute_value": "Must bring own bags/cart"}, {"attribute_key": "OFFERING", "attribute_value": "Clients can visit: Once a month"}, {"attribute_key": "INFO", "attribute_value": "Closed on major holidays"}, {"attribute_key": "REQUIREMENT", "attribute_value": "Registration required on site"}, {"attribute_key": "REQUIREMENT", "attribute_value": "A photo ID is required"}]}
